{"tid":1214760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個讀社工既學生，麻煩咁多位入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T21:39:54.000Z","uid":37430,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"241a3a6e76843ffa844368403d386ff26049cbb4","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"首先多謝咁多位以來所有發過既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住係海外做唔到d咩，呢幾日都係不停文宣<br />\n<br />\n真係辛苦了<br />\n<br />\n呢場預左係一場仗<br />\n<br />\n我就算隔住個mon都感受到......<br />\n<br />\n屋企人既極力反對，街上人既冷眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都會影響到我地<br />\n但係因為我地相信公義，先會出黎<br />\n尤其咁多位發夢行到最前既人，我琴日淨係睇片都喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用「槍林彈雨」黎形容一d都喊過份<br />\n<br />\n好，講返正題，我係想巴打們要知道，就係夢入面d 暴徒所做既一切，係會帶來精神創傷，老實講我淨係睇片都唔開心左成日，人神共憤<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴打由6月9號到而家都一直有時會突然好緊張，想嘔，坐立不安，食唔到，訓唔到因為一合埋眼就諗起，會有機會有ptsd (創傷後遺症）<br />\n由其中學生既你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請你地去返後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地先得10幾歲係絕對唔可以有呢種明明可以避免，但呢個仆街政府完全不顧及民意下留低比你地，我地所有人，同全香港呢一代所有人既精神創傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做唔到d乜主要係想開個po做一巴絲既心靈後盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我啱啱都開過一個post留左tg但冇人覆，可能呢幾日比較敏感大家都驚有鬼<br />\n<br />\n但我照擺多次，你想搵人傾我會陪你傾的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔需要證明我唔係鬼，亦都唔洗<br />\n<br />\n因為我相信連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲可以留言係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會一見到就覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇ac既你地，如果想搵我<br />\n<br />\nTg: leonleonthelion <br />\n<br />\n係tg搵我既唔洗同我提及政治立場，正係講下你「發完夢」有咩感覺，有咩想同我傾都可搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身體上既恢復可能係一日就得，但精神唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望咁多位巴絲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nI<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">It&rsquo;s ok to be not ok</span></span>"},{"pid":"aeeefd1e4bf5725e9f170384ce54456d402c8290","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e776cdfec38f9f08d33d80350a219b27cdd786cd","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfe791aaeb28cff80474ba6e31260892752165cf","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3e8c9b66bb2f3295aced7b2b1a0b8bf7af56c65","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f9f472e2b6b43181a4858c626f23782ccb8a3b0","tid":1214760,"uid":34777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n同為社工學生<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7c86acc445a7fbadc3642ce3f366094465c832","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9f472e2b6b43181a4858c626f23782ccb8a3b0","tid":1214760,"uid":34777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n同為社工學生<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗呢個都係我地可以做到既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b225741b0bc1be2093c1abed45866b96463170","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d273742245b492256f9068f6bad22c385743177","tid":1214760,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2e99e59caddd361089a7e7cda0ed38fcce5cbe2a","tid":1214760,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"避免有黑警偷資料<br />\n請記得發夢好啦"},{"pid":"8e562e2269cde2106feaa5c5f0f9457d5703dd78","tid":1214760,"uid":31906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"認真既 喊左幾次<br />\n喊完振作返 繼續抗爭"},{"pid":"76fc0ad221ef77c679e195ce75fdd1c380d868e8","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e99e59caddd361089a7e7cda0ed38fcce5cbe2a","tid":1214760,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"避免有黑警偷資料<br />\n請記得發夢好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我都好再三提醒我地都講下夢境炸"},{"pid":"b289c28b47737191b83c6dae5529318052ec81ee","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8e562e2269cde2106feaa5c5f0f9457d5703dd78","tid":1214760,"uid":31906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"認真既 喊左幾次<br />\n喊完振作返 繼續抗爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"每個人處理悲傷既能力唔同<br />\n發完一次夢唔敢再發既人，唔好去怪佢<br />\n<br />\n因為得佢自己先感受到果股情緒<br />\n<br />\n有人唔喊繼續戰鬥<br />\n有人喊繼次就起身<br />\n有人喊唔敢再起身<br />\n<br />\n我地要知道正正係呢d分別，我地係人，佢地係狗！<br />\n我地係冇被「訓練」過而上去<br />\n<br />\n抱歉，我本應都唔應該投放自己既情緒，但我都好嬲<br />\n<br />\n一個無忌極權要有幾陰質，幾折墮先做出d咁既事<br />\n<br />\n我地本來都唔應該要經歷一d如此撼動人心既事<br />\n<br />\n但無奈事實就係咁<br />\n亦都係我地點解要做社工<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a55f2ef791797fe0a83d097285021affed7f926","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28264d750db3bc8f88e63444e64e34ff53b0a05f","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3ae7ddbd1ea1ca03427ed29e1f0bf26693341c5","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1eedb38b05ea93076d8d7292772ffab4148115b2","tid":1214760,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c58ce4c7618df3593ca737b73e3c535d78ee2f6","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7a968334f4976e5b4822d7ae1b644163fe6ad9e","tid":1214760,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2ad8f1f38fbd72c695ed13828836408bbecff3","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:54:02.000Z","msg":"緊急醫療服務診所 <br />\n註冊護士+物理治療+心理學家 Standby 晚上8-10免費開放（今明兩晚一定有）<br />\n<br />\n如果有關節扭傷、肌肉韌帶拉傷、撞傷、瘀傷、傷口處理，這裡除了有註冊護士和物理治療師提供醫療服務和諮詢，同時有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">臨床心理學家提供情緒支援服務。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如有需要，請whatsapp 55930924預約，留下簡單名字（不用全名）及電語，可有免費諮詢<br />\n<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣堅拿道西15號永德大廈閣樓<br />\n<br />\nSource: Fact check 人員查詢"},{"pid":"81ddee89e9e84067f9a8054604605e031b78ae90","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdbbcb0909e739a50110812f64b1a8501b7ff8d4","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83c1d588fad9f52cbc1bd43ff5fce90f9a7078aa","tid":1214760,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply